  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 896.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The blockalteste there was the guy who was responsible with this group that is in this-- in this room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was good, this one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He tried to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't kick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't hit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just hit-- sometime he gave a kick, you know, but the kick is not the kick that kills you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some would give you a kick that you couldn't sit already for weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but the kapo-- the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were human.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If the Germans were stood, he make believe that he hits, that he's good because he wanted to have this job.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what they did-- their trick was too [? easy ?] the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're mixed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it's a new guy in a group of people Jewish, they take a Polack or a Czech.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if it's a Romanian, he takes a Hungarian to be a kapo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So for some reason, this makes a little hate between if you didn't listen to him right away and you didn't do the right way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he makes in front of the Germans that he is good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He is good, he is with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they liked him, so he had the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only way if the-- mine-- mine-- this was a blockalteste there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He loved me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He liked me very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saw-- he saw in me a little bit of-- I'm more a little a mensch with feelings, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was talking to him when he got a little-- I felt I have no afraid anymore for him that he's going to do something to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he listened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then I had a friend over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not this one.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
